# Normalize line endings.
# Auto-detect text files and store them as LF in the repository, and check
# them out as LF on all platforms. This silences the Windows
# "LF will be replaced by CRLF" warnings (these files are LF and run fine).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Generated/exported data is binary as far as Git is concerned (no EOL munging).
*.jasper binary
*.pdf binary
*.geojson binary
